I"h<p>前提是你以前已经安装过CocoaPods 
1、查看当前pod版本</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>pod --version
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>2、命令行安装</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>// 先更新gem
sudo gem update --system    // 需要漫长的等待
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>3、依次执行命令</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>brew install ruby
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem sources --remove https://rubygems.org/
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem sources -a https://ruby.taobao.org/
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>gem sources -l
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>*** CURRENT SOURCES ***

https://ruby.taobao.org/
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sudo gem install cocoapods      // 安装cocoapods
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>pod setup
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>##大功告成！！！</p>

:ET